{"tid":351660,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"NGT48討論區第9回：Online 36","createTime":"2017-08-08T08:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T08:47:38.000Z","uid":35157,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a270171d1f5f97f6e5a4908384e7cbe90ed92c7a","tid":351660,"uid":35157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:41:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">溫馨提示：<br />\n「FBI is watching you<br />\n    總有一天會長大」</span></span><br />\n<br />\nNGT48是日本一個由作詞家秋元康擔任製作人的女子偶像團體，主要的活動據點是日本北陸地方北端的主要城市新潟市。2015年8月21日於新潟市歷史博物館正式公開，自此展開活動。NGT48的團名是以根據地新潟的羅馬音簡寫（羅馬拼音為NIIGATA），是AKB48第7個姊妹團體、以及第5個國內姊妹團體。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ngt48.jp/resources/ckeditor_assets/000/012/001/12001-ngt48_profile_up.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fngt48.jp%2Fresources%2Fckeditor_assets%2F000%2F012%2F001%2F12001-ngt48_profile_up.png%3F&h=30ec03b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/b5paOGf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fb5paOGf.jpg&h=92170641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1362pjmv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1362pjmv&h=6ef4f2e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNGT48 1st Anniversary - <span style=\"color: red;\">好評發售中</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 什麼是NGT48?<br />\nNGT48 係 AKB48 Group 位於新潟的姊妹團，成立於2015年，到今年2017年4月正式出道，現任隊長係北原里英，劇場支配人係今村悅朗。趁早推，此團日後必紅。<br />\n<br />\n2. 這po有沒有版規?<br />\n無，我地好自由。不過請尊重成員及唔好人身攻擊其他會員。另外，新人加入時如有心儀的推請講低，方便大家討論。<br />\n<br />\n3. 如果討論其他48G姊妹團或46友團會否引起世界大戰？<br />\n絕對唔會，不用分哪麼細，錢都是肥秋賺。<br />\n<br />\n4. NGT有咩好歌推介?<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n-iXRXpfVTs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn-iXRXpfVTs&d=DSj0j%2Fs1g7mKpXqlN9%2FFvr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=ae818b65\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n-iXRXpfVTs</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 除了NGT48，有沒有其他推介？<br />\n全個AKB48 Group都好正，OK？<br />\n<br />\n歡迎新人加入<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">舊po回帶：</span><br />\n第1回：有冇 NGT48 Fans?? <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/273226/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/273226/</a><br />\n第2回：村雲生日快樂 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/308883/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/308883/</a><br />\n第3回︰趁早加推NGT <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/320724\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/320724</a><br />\n第4回︰柏木&amp;太野生日快樂 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/326223\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/326223</a><br />\n第5回︰請支持奈良未遙 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/333053\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/333053</a><br />\n第6回︰本家大米心戰王連成一線 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/338526\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/338526</a><br />\n第7回︰型男索女都加推NGT了 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/342680\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/342680</a><br />\n第8回︰今年米團首推改 明年海軍復誰在 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/345651\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/345651</a><br />\n第9回︰每日都幻想與你海灘慢步 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/349635\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/349635</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n開 Po Template: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1AKl4mAOiC9M4zQyX-zfgspPcXmM3HjSq3fi3R-9j_yc/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1AKl4mAOiC9M4zQyX-zfgspPcXmM3HjSq3fi3R-9j_yc%2Fedit&d=DSj0j%2Fs1g7mKpXqlN9%2FFvr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=51f04bf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1AKl4mAOiC9M4zQyX-zfgspPcXmM3HjSq3fi3R-9j_yc/edit</a>"},{"pid":"4aeda5fb1020ab8ae9a0c631a812346b337edd3c","tid":351660,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:42:27.000Z","msg":"第10回喎清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9beeb0b0a6d5ae3161a9d5bd1248590402c877","tid":351660,"uid":98129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:42:44.000Z","msg":"C貢快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ab9e1f466fa1c83604de19b5652f75b6134e91","tid":351660,"uid":20131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:43:59.000Z","msg":"9 ?"},{"pid":"8119520fb299e000a39ce8aa3757f0854c6401bb","tid":351660,"uid":35157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:44:36.000Z","msg":"Ctrl C+V Failed<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a845277bb7d11162c03facdce5ae59d52d5fb6","tid":351660,"uid":67331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:46:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">開過啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n10 呀"},{"pid":"ca27a0cba3253b9b58bd84eebdf3e784873240ba","tid":351660,"uid":98129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:46:58.000Z","msg":"第5條問題啊C"},{"pid":"9e9c34993749b2cfadfe265128827d2964d7b591","tid":351660,"uid":35157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:47:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/351664/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/351664/page/1</a>　<br />\nFML"},{"pid":"c12ec30a483335846f30e6c45a17597cdca42e0c","tid":351660,"uid":20131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:47:38.000Z","msg":"無左其他推薦嗰part"}]}